**Occult Wolf** | Werewolf Group | Transformation
__Basics__
The Occult Wolf is a wolfpack member who is a part of the cult.
__Details__
If any of the members of the cult group would become werewolf-aligned, their role changes to Occult Wolf.
The Occult Wolf is a member of the cult: they can vote on the cult's kill polls. The Occult Wolf does not retain any other abilities its previous role had.
The Occult Wolf is strongly disguised as their previous role.

__Simplified__
The Occult Wolf is a wolfpack member who is a part of the cult.
